      *          계열기업군코드
           MOVE  CO-CHA-00
             TO  OT-AFFLT-CORP-GROUP-CD(1:2)
           MOVE  WK-H-O-KIS-GROUP-CD
             TO  OT-AFFLT-CORP-GROUP-CD(3:3)

      *          기업규모구분
           MOVE  WK-H-O-CORP-SCAL-DSTCD
             TO  OT-CORP-SCAL-DSTCD

      *          등록직원번호
           MOVE  WK-JOB-EMPID
             TO  OT-REGI-EMPID

      *          등록년월일
           MOVE  BICOM-TRAN-BASE-YMD
             TO  OT-REGI-YMD

      *          변경여부
           MOVE  CO-CHA-0
             TO  OT-MODFI-YN

      *  채무자명　전자　변환　변수　
           MOVE  WK-H-O-KIS-ENTP-ABRVN-NAME
